=====================================================
|ID|OPERATOR             |NAME|EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------
|0 |EXCHANGE IN REMOTE   |    |5       |8           |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE|    |5       |6           |
|2 |  └─MERGE GROUP BY   |    |5       |3           |
|3 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN|T1  |5       |3           |
=====================================================
