|11|    │   │     │ └─SUBPLAN FILTER     |          |1       |5           |
|12|    │   │     │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |AP        |1       |3           |
|13|    │   │     │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |AU_COMPANY|1       |3           |
|14|    │   │     └─SUBPLAN SCAN         |VIEW3     |1       |3           |
|15|    │   │       └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |AP        |1       |3           |
